title: BREAKING! Uncounted Votes Now Found! | Ep 66
description: Steven looks at the latest fake hate crimes, the possible impeachment of Governor Whitmer, and other hypocrisy from Democrats over COVID restrictions. He then continues Fraud Week, with a comprehensive look at the voting irregularities in Georgia. He finishes by explaining the problems of Biden's proposed student loan debt forgiveness.
